node.text: Thank you for a million views on my baby mama dance 🙈 I had so much fun with this and yes Princess Batman is safe and sound in there! Currently at #39WeeksPregnant and I feel like this is THE week 🙈 fingers crossed. Thank y’all for the support ❤️

node.text: Feeling like me again 💕 I sometimes still feel like my back is a noodle and I’m squishy where my giant belly used to be, BUT I’m happy and healthy along with my beautiful family. Couldn’t ask for anything more. I do miss eating for 2– wait who am I kidding..I’ll still kill a dozen donuts in a heartbeat. 🍩 mmm donuts...what’s your favorite flavor?!

node.text: Happy birthday to my favorite person 🖤 another year spent full of contagious laughter, beautiful babies and one too many late nights watching trash reality tv 🤷🏻‍♀️ I love this man more than words could ever describe. He’s got a heart of gold and never stops giving 10000% of it to our family. Happy birthday my Juggi! Here’s to many more spent together 🥳

node.text: Yesterday our little blessing came into this world. Amélie Irene Hildén, welcome to our loving family. I am so lucky to be your mother and give you a beautiful safe life with your amazing father @jukkadudeson and your older siblings 💕 you are officially apart of the Hildén circus!

node.text: Ready whenever you are baby girl 💕#40weeks 🤰🏻
